title: [Ocoma Vale]
description: A small stream borders the grassy glen, wending along the edge of a heavy thicket of alder and modwir trees.  Small golden butterflies dance their way through the meadow and into the forest, flitting frenetically as they evade imaginary perils.

A small stream borders the grassy glen, wending along the edge of a heavy thicket of alder and modwir trees.  Tiny fireflies dance their way through the meadow and into the forest, flitting frenetically as they evade imaginary perils.
